  <h2>
    <span class="">喜欢读&#34;古代汉语（第一册）&#34;的人也喜欢</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <div class="content clearfix">
      
      <dl class="">
        <dt>
            <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1042011/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '1042011', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})"><img class="m_sub_img" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/spic/s10266048.jpg"/></a>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1042011/" onclick="moreurl(this, {'total': 10, 'clicked': '1042011', 'pos': 0, 'identifier': 'book-rec-books'})" class="">
            古代汉语（第二册）
          </a>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      
