              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21619139/" class="">左传</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/canopy/" class=" " title="扇子">扇子</a>
                (少折腾，多做点力所能及的事情。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21619139">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21619139/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p21619139-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 
这篇是不是左传必选呀</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21619139/">(<span class="">5回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-10-09 19:26</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
